---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="flex min-h-screen items-center bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-7xl gap-8 px-4 lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="text-center lg:col-span-5 lg:text-left">
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-700 md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
          Accede a una beca y transforma tu futuro
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-primary-800">
          Apoyamos a jovenes de areas rurales en Guatemala para acceder a educacion y oportunidades reales.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row lg:justify-start">
          <a href="/aplicacion" class="rounded-lg bg-primary-700 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-800">
            Aplicar a beca
          </a>
          <a href="#como-aplicar" class="rounded-lg border border-primary-300 bg-secondary-soft px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-primary-800 hover:bg-primary-100">
            Ver requisitos
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center lg:col-span-7">
        <img class="w-full rounded-lg border border-secondary/60 shadow-sm" src="/home1.JPG" alt="Estudiantes beneficiados por la fundacion" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="como-aplicar" class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto mb-12 max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-700">
          Como aplicar a la beca
        </h2>
        <p class="text-primary-800">
          Sigue estos pasos para iniciar tu proceso.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 text-center md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-700">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="rgb(255, 255, 255)" d="M448 75.2l0 361.7c0 24.3-19 43.2-43.2 43.2l-361.6 0C19.3 480 0 461.4 0 436.8L0 75.2C0 51.1 18.8 32 43.2 32l361.7 0c24 0 43.1 18.8 43.1 43.2zM410.7 436.8l0-361.6c0-3-2.6-5.8-5.8-5.8l-9.3 0-110.3 74.6-61.3-49.9-61.2 49.9-110.3-74.7-9.3 0c-3.2 0-5.8 2.8-5.8 5.8l0 361.7c0 3 2.6 5.8 5.8 5.8l361.7 0c3.2 .1 5.8-2.7 5.8-5.8zM150.2 186l0 37-73.5 0 0-37 73.5 0zm0 74.4l0 37.3-73.5 0 0-37.3 73.5 0zm11.1-147.3l54-43.7-118.5 0 64.5 43.7zm210 72.9l0 37-196 0 0-37 196 0zm0 74.4l0 37.3-196 0 0-37.3 196 0zM286.7 113.1l64.5-43.7-118.4 0 53.9 43.7zM371.3 335l0 37.3-99.4 0 0-37.3 99.4 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">1. Llena el formulario</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-800">
            Completa tu informacion personal y academica.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-700">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="rgb(255, 255, 255)" d="M96 0C60.7 0 32 28.7 32 64l0 384c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64l180 0c-22.7-31.5-36-70.2-36-112 0-100.6 77.4-183.2 176-191.3l0-38.1c0-17-6.7-33.3-18.7-45.3L290.7 18.7C278.7 6.7 262.5 0 245.5 0L96 0zM357.5 176L264 176c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24L240 58.5 357.5 176zM576 400a144 144 0 1 0 -288 0 144 144 0 1 0 288 0zm-86.6-60.9c7.1 5.2 8.7 15.2 3.5 22.3l-64 88c-2.8 3.8-7 6.2-11.7 6.5s-9.3-1.3-12.6-4.6l-40-40c-6.2-6.2-6.2-16.4 0-22.6s16.4-6.2 22.6 0l26.8 26.8 53-72.9c5.2-7.1 15.2-8.7 22.4-3.5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">2. Adjunta documentos</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-800">
            Envia los requisitos solicitados.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-700">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="rgb(255, 255, 255)" d="M48 195.8l209.2 86.1c9.8 4 20.2 6.1 30.8 6.1s21-2.1 30.8-6.1l242.4-99.8c9-3.7 14.8-12.4 14.8-22.1s-5.8-18.4-14.8-22.1L318.8 38.1C309 34.1 298.6 32 288 32s-21 2.1-30.8 6.1L14.8 137.9C5.8 141.6 0 150.3 0 160L0 456c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24s24-10.7 24-24l0-260.2zm48 71.7L96 384c0 53 86 96 192 96s192-43 192-96l0-116.6-142.9 58.9c-15.6 6.4-32.2 9.7-49.1 9.7s-33.5-3.3-49.1-9.7L96 267.4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">3. Proceso de seleccion</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-800">
            Evaluamos tu perfil y te contactamos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="/aplicacion" class="rounded-lg bg-primary-700 px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-800">
          Iniciar aplicacion
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-secondary-soft">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-700">
        Historias que inspiran
      </h2>
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-primary-600 bg-primary-700 text-white shadow-lg">
          <img
            class="aspect-square w-full object-cover"
            src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/bonnie-green.png"
            alt="Maria Lopez"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="mb-5 text-primary-50">
              "Gracias a la beca pude continuar mis estudios y ahora soy profesional."
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-white">Maria Lopez</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-primary-600 bg-primary-700 text-white shadow-lg">
          <img
            class="aspect-square w-full object-cover"
            src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/jese-leos.png"
            alt="Juan Perez"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="mb-5 text-primary-50">
              "El apoyo cambio completamente mi vida y la de mi familia."
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-white">Juan Perez</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-primary-600 bg-primary-700 text-white shadow-lg">
          <img
            class="aspect-square w-full object-cover"
            src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/michael-gouch.png"
            alt="Ana Garcia"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="mb-5 text-primary-50">
              "Hoy tengo oportunidades que antes parecian imposibles."
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-white">Ana Garcia</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 py-16 text-center sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-700">+1000</p>
        <p class="text-primary-800">Jovenes becados</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-700">+3</p>
        <p class="text-primary-800">Departamentos</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-700">+20</p>
        <p class="text-primary-800">Anos de impacto</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-700">
          Quienes somos
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-primary-800">
          Somos una fundacion comprometida con el desarrollo educativo en Guatemala, enfocada en brindar oportunidades a jovenes con alto potencial.
        </p>
        <a href="/nosotros" class="font-medium text-primary-700 hover:underline">
          Conocer mas
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-primary-700">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-extrabold text-white md:text-4xl">
        Tu futuro puede empezar hoy
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-white">
        Aplica a una beca y cambia tu historia.
      </p>
      <a href="/aplicacion" class="rounded-lg bg-white px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-primary-700 hover:bg-primary-100">
        Aplicar ahora
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
